Yes, I can surely answer that question.

Bayern Munich has won the most DFB-Pokal titles with a total of 20 wins, making them the most successful team in the competition's history. The earliest triumph for Bayern came in 1957, and the most recent in 2019-20 season. Dortmund has won eight times, Werder Bremen six times, while Schalke and Hamburg each have won 5 times in the competition.
